Model Structure Planning

Membership
    -slug
    -type(free pro enterprise)
    -price
    -stripe plan id



UserMembership
    -user           (foreign key to the default user)
    -stripe customer id
    -membership type     (foreign key to the membership)



Subscription
    -user membership
    -stripe subscription        (foreign key to the Usermembership)
    -active



Course
    -slug
    -title
    -description
    -allowed membership         (foreign key to the membership)


Lesson
    -slug
    -title
    -Course           (foreign key to the courses)
    -position
    -video
    -thumbnail